nodes.title: Setup and Tips
widgets_values:
On first use:
- select models and VAE
- select a default LoRA in each Load LoRA node
- select an upscale model
- add an image in each of the Load Images nodes (purple nodes)
- add a default image batch in the Load Image Batch node
- select the batch_size in CR Aspect Ratio SDXL
- set the filename_prefix in Save Image to your preferred sub-folder
- save a copy to use as a template

Tips:
- Notes can be opened by clicking on the dots (green nodes)
- Each optional component can be bypassed using logic switches (red nodes)
- The default setting for all logic switches is OFF (1)
- Use Comfyroll Manager to find any missing custom nodes
- Right-click on nodes and select Pin to pin/unpin the node
